        <h3>Expandable 2200+ Plant Database<br>
        To help you find the perfect plants for your garden.</h3>
        <p align="center"><img src="gifs/image14.gif"
        alt="3D Landscape Plant Profile" width="334" height="250"
        naturalsizeflag="3"></p>
        <blockquote>
            <p>3D Landscape's plant database contains more than
            2200 popular trees, shrubs, flowers, and ground
            covers that you can specify in your landscape. The
            powerful database quickly find the right plants based
            on your garden climate and your personal preferences.</p>
            <p>You can even add your own plants - right into the
            database - to personalize your planting information.
            Plus you can import additional plant to expand the
            plant database. Garden Encyclopedia, for example,
            will nearly double the number plants in the database.</p>
        </blockquote>
        <p align="center"><a href="3dlandm.htm">Return to 3D
        Landscape main page.</a></p>
