<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/pubscomm.html">International Communications</A><BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/pubsecur.html">National and International
Security</A><BR>
<li>Regional Studies<BR>
<UL>
<li><a href="http://www.csis.org/html/pubsafri.html">Africa</a>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/pubsamer.html">Americas</A><BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/pubsasia.html">Asia and the Pacific</A><BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/pubseuro.html">Europe--East and West</A><BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/pubsruss.html">Russia and Eurasia</A></ul>
<li><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/newpubs.html"><b>New Publications</b></A>
</UL></ul><P>

If you are interested in purchasing a CSIS publication, please use our <a href="http://www.csis.org/html/faxform.html">mail/fax order form</a>.  Or, contact Heidi Shinn in the Publications Sales Office at (202) 775-3119, or send email to
<A HREF="mailto:books@csis.org">books@csis.org</A>.  To write
for information, the address is:<P> <CENTER><B>CSIS</B><BR>
