<HEAD><TITLE>CSIS Business Alert</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<BODY><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<P ALIGN="center"><img
src="http://www.csis.org/images/3pubs.gif"></P>

<img vspace=20 src="http://www.csis.org/images/alert.gif">

<B>
<p>

The CSIS Business Alert is a one-page fax publication produced by the Office of the Director of Studies.  It summarizes CSIS expert opinion on current business issues.</B><P>
<hr>

<UL><h4>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.csis.org/html/alert20.html">#20:
The Era of Entitlements</A>
