<H1>PacNet Newsletter</H1>
<HR><P>The <I>PacNet Newsletter</I> is a weekly publication generated from a
network of policy research institutes by <a href="http://www.csis.org/html/2pacfor.html">Pacific Forum CSIS</a>.  The brief newsletter is designed to
facilitate communication on timely and fast breaking events in the region
and to serve as a vehicle for sharing research results and analyses.<P><HR><P>

