<head>
<title>What is the mission of CSIS?</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor=#ffffff>
<p align="center"><img src="http://www.csis.org/images/3missio.gif"></p>
<h1>What is the mission of CSIS?</h1>

     <b>Policy impact is the basic mission of CSIS.</b>  Our goal 
is to inform 
and shape selected policy decisions in government and the private 
sector to meet the 
increasingly complex and difficult challenges that leaders will 
confront in the next century. 

