<HEAD><TITLE>CSIS Europe Publications</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<a href="http://www.csis.org/cgi-bin/imagemap/button"><p align="center"><IMG width=515 height=35 border=0 SRC="http://www.csis.org/images/button.gif" ISMAP></p></a>

<p align="center"><img
src="http://www.csis.org/images/3pubs.gif"></p>
<H2><p align="center">Europe</p></H2>

<hr>

<table cellpadding=20><tr>
<td width=150 valign=top>
<font size="2">
<i>Titles:</i><p>
<a href="#france">Does France Still Count?</a>  The French Role in the New Europe<p>
<a href="#ethnic">Ethnic Politics in Eastern Europe:</a>
A Guide to Nationality Policies, Organizations, and Parties<p>
<a href="#transatl">Making Transatlantic Defense Cooperation Work</a><p>
<a href="#migration">Migration and the New Europe</a><p>
<a href="#nordic">Nordic-Baltic Security:</a>
An International Perspective<p>
