			The Political-Military Studies Program will host a monthly forum intended to give senior military, business, academic, and governmental leaders an 			opportunity to discuss U.S. policies and issues of strategic importance. The 			speaker for January is the Secretary of the Army, the Honorable Togo 			West.<br>
