<HEAD>
<TITLE> The B'Tselem Automated Electronic Mailing List </TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY  BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000">

<CENTER>
<I>
<FONT SIZE="+3"><B> The B'Tselem Automated Electronic Mailing List </B></FONT>
</I>
</CENTER>
<HR>
<P>
<B>B'Tselem</B> has an automated electronic mailing list, which will
distribute 
press releases and public statements, as well as provide information on
advocacy campaigns.
<P>
If you wish to <FONT SIZE=+1><B>subscribe</B></FONT> to the mailing 
list, send an E-Mail with the subject: <FONT COLOR="red"><B>subscribe</B></FONT> 
to the following address:
<P>
<CENTER>
          <A HREF="mailto:btselem-L-request@netgate.net">btselem-L-request@netgate.net</A>
</CENTER>
<P>
 
If you wish to <FONT SIZE=+1><B>unsubscribe</B></FONT> from the mailing 
list, send an E-Mail with the subject: <FONT COLOR="red"><B>unsubscribe</B></FONT>
to the same address.
