<P>
<FONT SIZE=+2.5> Solidarity Visit to Gaza of Palestinian and Israeli Faculty</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<HR>
BíTselem is organizing a trip to Gaza in order to call attention to the problem 
of Gaza students who are prevented from studying in their West Bank universities.  The trip will consist of 
faculty members from Israeli and Palestinian universities and will take place in mid-January.
<P>
Faculty members who are interested in participating are requested to notify Eitan Felner at B'Tselem:
