<hr>
<h3>Japanese Forestry Literature Information System(FOLIS)</h3>
<img src="sym-l.GIF">
<FONT SIZE=4>
<p>
</CENTER>
<B>Introduction of FOLIS</B>
<P>
This database consists of approximately 400 domestic publications 
selected from amongst those in the Institute's library. These and 
articles relating to forestry and forest products were selected and 
classified by major topic according to the ODC system. 
Records consisting of the keywords for each document were then entered
into the computer.
<p>
<HR>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="telnet://cs.ffpri.affrc.go.jp">Access to FOLIS</A>
<UL>
- When the login prompt appear, please type in "folis"-
</UL></UL>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="folis_manual.html">User's Manual(in Japanese)</A>
</UL>
