<title>FORESTRY WHITE PAPER</title>
<pre>
       <h2>FORESTRY WHITE PAPER</h2>
       <h4>Fiscal Year 1994</h4>
       <h3>SUMMRY</h3>

<img src="white-p_94/w-p_photo.gif">
          <h2>Forestry Agency , JAPAN</h2>
</pre>
<HR>
<pre>
This is the summry of the "Annual Report on Trends of Forestry
(Fiscal year 1994)"and "Forestry Policy Actions to Be Taken in
Foscal Year 1995"which were laid before the Diet in conformity
with the Forestry Basic Law(1964),Article 9,Clause 1 and 2 
respectively,and were approved on 21th April 1995.


<h5>Cover Page Photo : Sakae-mura,Nagano prefecture</h5>
<P>
<HR>
<pre><br>
<B><h3>CONTENTS</B></h3>
<br>
<A HREF="white-p_94/t0.html"><B>Prologue</B></A>
<p> 
<A HREF="white-p_94/t1.html"><B>1. FOR FURTHER DEVELOPMENT OF FOREST CULTURE</B></A> 
 1 Forest Culture 
 2 Relationship of Japanese with Forest and Wood 
 3 Development of Forest Culture in Modern Japan
 4 Status Quo of Forestry, Wocd Industries, and Upstream 
   Villages which carry Forest Culture
 5 For Further Development of Forest Culture
 
<A HREF="white-p_94/t2.html"><B>2. FOREST, FORESTRY AND UPSTREAM VILLAGES</B></A> 
 1 Forest in Japan 
 2 Recent Trends in Forestry Production 
 3 Recent Trends in Forest Management 
 4 Recent Trends in Upstream Villages 

<A HREF="white-p_94/t3.html"><B>3. ROLE OF NATIONAL FOREST OPERATION AND MANAGEMENT REFORM</B></A>
 1 Role of National Forest Operation and Progress of 
   its Undertakings 
 2 Implementation of Management Reform 

<A HREF="white-p_94/t4.html"><B>4. WOOD DEMAND/SUPPLY AND WOOD INDUSTRIES</B></A> 
 1 Recent Trends in Wood Demand and Supply 
 2 Recent Trends in Wood Prices
 3 Recent Trends in Wood Industries

<A HREF="white-p_94/t5.html"><B>5. WORLD FOREST RESOURCES AND JAPAN'S INTERNATIONAL 
   FOREST/FORESTRY COOPERATION</B></A> 
 1 State of World Forest Resources, Sustainable Forest 
   Management, and Recent Trends in Wood Trade 
 2 Japan's Effort for International Forest and Forestly 
   Cooperation

<A HREF="white-p_94/t6.html"><B>EPILOGUE</B></A>

<A HREF="white-p_94/t7.html"><B>FORESTRY POLICY ACTIONS TAKEN IN 1994</B></A> 

<A HREF="white-p_94/t8.html"><B>FORESTRY POLICY ACTIONS TO BE TAKEN IN 1995</B></A>
</pre>
