<pre>
CIFOR - Center for International Forestry Research 
FY    - Japanese Fiscal Year (1st April - 31st March of the 
        following year) 
FAO   - Food and Agriculture Organization ofthe United Nations 
GATT  - General Agreement on Tariff and Trade 
ICRAE - International Center for Research in Agroforestry 
ITTO  - International Tropical Timber Organization 
JICA  - Japan International Cooperation Agency 
MAFF  - Ministry of Agriculture. Forestry and Fisheries 
NGO   - Non Government Organization 
TFAP  - Tropical Forests Action Program 
